'''TurboTax'''是[[美國|美國]]提供[[報稅_(美國)|報稅服務]]的稅務軟件。該軟件由[[Intuit|Intuit公司]]開發。Turbotax在同類服務軟件的供應市場佔有領導地位。其他同類型的服務軟件包括[[H&R_Block_Tax_Software|H&R Block Tax Software]]及[[TaxAct|TaxAct]]。<ref name=NYTPaces>{{cite news |first = Tim |last = Gray |date = 2012-02-11 |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/business/yourtaxes/tax-software-is-put-through-the-paces-review.html?_r=0/ |title = Taking Tax Software for a Walk |work = The New York Times |accessdate = 2022-05-18 |archive-date = 2022-03-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220322101007/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/business/yourtaxes/tax-software-is-put-through-the-paces-review.html?_r=0%2F }}</ref>TurboTax最初於1984年由Michael A. Chipman所成立的Chipsoft所開發，後來於1993年公司被售予[[Intuit|Intuit]]。<ref>{{cite web |url = https://people.forbes.com/profile/michael-a-chipman/12618 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090516184756/http://people.forbes.com/profile/michael-a-chipman/12618 |archive-date = 2009-05-16 |title = Michael Chipman |department = People |work = Forbes |date = 2012-04-18 |access-date = 2013-12-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://articles.latimes.com/1993-09-02/business/fi-30906_1_intuit-stock |title = Intuit, Chipsoft Agree to Merge in $225-Million Deal |last = Groves |first = Martha |date = 1993-09-02 |website = Los Angeles Times |access-date = 2016-12-29 |archive-date = 2016-12-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161230155850/http://articles.latimes.com/1993-09-02/business/fi-30906_1_intuit-stock }}</ref>

